moduleName: Google Auth / OAuth2 / Token Info / Create
description: Retrieves information about an OAuth 2.0 token, such as its validity, associated scopes, and expiration time. Useful for debugging and verifying token details.

schema.description: OAuth 2 access token. Most APIs require `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/documents` scope. Google Auth / Service Account Token can be used to obtain a valid access token.
API key can be generated in Google Developer Console in APIs & Services section. Leave blank if OAuth access token is used.
